page.title: 10 Streethouse
page.content: Streethouse is a small village with a lot of residential property there. Most of the property is an estate with council houses.A lot of the houses are being renovated as they were run down due to vandalism and erosion. Streethouse lies about one and a half miles south-east of Normanton. Streethouse has a public park,a Shop which sells the family needs, there is a church,a bank,a betting shop,a takeaway hot food shop,and at the moment they are building a B.M.X track.The village itself isn't very clean, there is a lot of letters about,and a lot of graffiti on walls.There is a beck with bits of old prams, junk ect.
